name: Gerard Dacudao
text: Roy, tandaan mo nasa MM ka. My surveys included Visayas and Mindanao.  However, MM will aslo go for Du30.  At least may idea ka na sino ang malamang mananalo.  Diba?  Sarap ng feeling.
